title: Paris FATF Plenary: Global Implementation of Virtual Asset Standards Remains ‘Relatively Poor’
description: The third plenary of the Financial Action Task Force (FATF), held in Paris, found a lack of global adoption of the virtual asset recommendations established by the institution. According to evaluations, almost three-quarters of the jurisdictions are partially compliant or non-compliant with these recommendations.
